---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="About | Karma & Code" description="Learn about Neon Dev Blog and what we cover">
  <div class="min-h-screen flex flex-col bg-background text-foreground">
    <Header />

    <main class="flex-1 container py-16 max-w-4xl">
      <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold mb-8 neon-gradient-text neon-glow-green">
        About This Blog
      </h1>

      <div class="space-y-6 text-lg text-foreground/90 leading-relaxed">
        <p>
          Welcome to <span class="text-primary font-semibold">Neon Dev Blog</span>, a technical
          blog dedicated to exploring the cutting edge of software development. Here, we dive deep
          into modern web technologies, best practices, and architectural patterns that shape the
          future of software engineering.
        </p>

        <p>
          Our focus areas include <span class="text-secondary">React</span>, <span class="text-primary">TypeScript</span>,
          modern CSS frameworks like <span class="text-accent">Tailwind CSS</span>, and web architecture
          patterns that enable developers to build scalable, maintainable applications.
        </p>

        <div class="bg-card/30 backdrop-blur-sm border border-border/50 rounded-lg p-8 my-8 neon-border-glow">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4 neon-glow-cyan text-secondary">
            What We Cover
          </h2>
          <ul class="space-y-3 text-foreground">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-primary text-xl">▸</span>
              <span>Modern frontend frameworks and libraries</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-secondary text-xl">▸</span>
              <span>TypeScript patterns and best practices</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-accent text-xl">▸</span>
              <span>CSS architecture and design systems</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-primary text-xl">▸</span>
              <span>Web performance optimization</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <span class="text-secondary text-xl">▸</span>
              <span>Software architecture and design patterns</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <p>
          This blog is built with passion for clean code and modern aesthetics. The neon theme
          reflects our belief that developer tools and content can be both functional and
          visually striking.
        </p>

        <p class="text-muted-foreground italic">
          Built with Astro, Tailwind CSS 4, TypeScript, and a love for neon aesthetics.
        </p>
      </div>
    </main>

    <Footer />
  </div>
</Layout>
